# Copy to .deploy-env and set your SMB target. .deploy-env is not committed.
# Deploy sends dist/ to the share. Server path is /data/websites/<sitename> (e.g. /data/websites/gorfed.net).

# Option A: Already-mounted SMB share (mount point on your Mac; server path is /data/websites/*)
# SMB_MOUNT=/Volumes/data/websites/gorfed.net

# Option B: Mount by URL (mount_smbfs will prompt for password if not set)
# SMB_URL=//username@hostname/sharename
# SMB_MOUNT_POINT=/Volumes/gorfed-deploy
# SMB_PASSWORD=yourpassword

# Public Web3Forms access key used on contact page (injected at build time into dist/contact.html)
# WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=6e1c5c65-1807-44a7-8460-b72e510f94e5
